                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18260406-307-off1648 t18260406-307-cd1649"></join>, 6ozs. weight of tea, value 9d., the goods of the 
                     <persName id="t18260406-307-victim1649" type="victimName">
                        <rs id="t18260406-307-viclabel1650" type="occupation">United Company of Merchants, trading to the East Indies</rs>
